<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nael Talbi | Portfolio SIO SISR</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* === VARIABLES & RESET === */
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #050505;
            --card-bg: #111111;
            --border-color: #222222;
            --text-main: #ededed;
            --text-muted: #888888;
            --accent-glow: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        /* === TYPOGRAPHIE === */
        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        /* === NAVIGATION (GLASSMORPHISM) === */
        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 10%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        nav { display: flex; gap: 30px; }

        nav a {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover { color: var(--text-main); }

        /* === HERO SECTION === */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 10%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #1a1a1a 0%, var(--bg-dark) 60%);
        }

        .hero-badge {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--text-main);
            color: var(--bg-dark);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #ffffff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-main);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: #555;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        /* === SECTIONS COMMUNES === */
        section { padding: 100px 10%; }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        /* === COMPÉTENCES === */
        .skills-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .skill-tag {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .skill-tag:hover {
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-color: #38bdf8;
            background: var(--accent-glow);
        }

        /* === PROJETS === */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(800px circle at var(--mouse-x) var(--mouse-y), rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent 40%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #444;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* === FOOTER === */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 10%;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* === ANIMATIONS (JS) === */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { display: none; } /* On cache le menu sur mobile pour faire simple */
            .btn-group { flex-direction: column; }
            section { padding: 80px 5%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <a href="#" class="logo">Nael<span class="text-gradient">Talbi</span></a>
        <nav>
            <a href="#accueil">Accueil</a>
            <a href="#competences">Compétences</a>
            <a href="#projets">Projets</a>
            <a href="mailto:ton.email@exemple.com">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="accueil" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-badge">Étudiant BTS SIO - Option SISR</div>
        <h1 class="reveal">Architecte de votre <br><span class="text-gradient">Infrastructure IT</span></h1>
        <p class="reveal">Passionné par l'administration système, les réseaux et la sécurité. Découvrez comment je construis et maintiens des environnements informatiques fiables.</p>
        
        <div class="btn-group reveal">
            <a href="#projets" class="btn btn-primary">Voir mes projets</a>
            <a href="cv.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">Télécharger mon CV</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="competences" class="reveal">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Expertise Technique</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="skills-container">
            <span class="skill-tag">Windows Server</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Active Directory / GPO</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">GNU/Linux (Debian)</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Routage & Switching</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">GLPI / Ticketing</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Virtualisation (Hyper-V / VMware)</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">OPNsense / Pare-feu</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Scripts PowerShell / Bash</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="projets">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
            <h2>Réalisations & Projets</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card reveal">
                <div class="card-icon">🔐</div>
                <h3>Domaine Active Directory</h3>
                <p>Création d'un environnement d'entreprise simulé. Déploiement de contrôleurs de domaine, gestion des droits utilisateurs (OU), et automatisation de la sécurité via des Stratégies de Groupe (GPO).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card reveal">
                <div class="card-icon">🎫</div>
                <h3>Intégration GLPI</h3>
                <p>Déploiement d'un serveur LAMP pour héberger la solution GLPI. Configuration du système de Helpdesk, création de règles d'affectation automatique et gestion de l'inventaire parc avec l'agent OCS/FusionInventory.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card reveal">
                <div class="card-icon">🌐</div>
                <h3>Architecture Réseau Sécurisée</h3>
                <p>Conception d'une topologie réseau complète. Segmentation du trafic par VLANs, configuration de routeurs, et mise en place d'un pare-feu OPNsense pour sécuriser l'accès WAN et filtrer les flux LAN.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card reveal">
                <div class="card-icon">💾</div>
                <h3>Sauvegarde & Redondance</h3>
                <p>Mise en place de solutions de tolérance aux pannes. Configuration de baies de stockage (RAID) et planification de routines de sauvegarde automatisées pour garantir la continuité de service (PRA/PCA).</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Nael Talbi. Hébergé sur le Cloud via GitHub Pages.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function reveal() {
            var reveals = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal");
            for (var i = 0; i < reveals.length; i++) {
                var windowHeight = window.innerHeight;
                var elementTop = reveals[i].getBoundingClientRect().top;
                var elementVisible = 100;
                if (elementTop < windowHeight - elementVisible) {
                    reveals[i].classList.add("active");
                }
            }
        }
        window.addEventListener("scroll", reveal);
        reveal(); // Déclencher au chargement
    </script>
</body>
</html>
